description: Keep Figma Code Connect and UI primitives in lockstep
globs: "components/ui/**/*.{ts,tsx},lib/design-system.ts,docs/design-system/**/*.md"
alwaysApply: false
---

# Figma Code Connect workflow

- For any primitive API change, keep parity across:
  - `components/ui/*`
  - `lib/design-system.ts`
  - `docs/design-system/figma-code-connect-mapping.md`

- Before adding a new component in Figma workflows:
  - check existing design system components first (`search_design_system`)
  - keep variant names equal to code variant names
  - keep slot names aligned to `data-slot` anatomy

- If variant names diverge between Figma and code, normalize code and mapping docs in the same change.

- Never introduce hardcoded palette colors in primitives to satisfy design mocks.
  Convert to semantic token usage in `app/globals.css` first.
